        <h2>Project Background</h2>
            <p>As a capstone in the Information Technology minor program I was given the opportunity to work on tech projects for a real-world client. My group matched with the Hollander Makerspace on Michigan State’s campus. The Makerspace provides expertise and infrastructure for discovery and creation, they are most known for their 3D-printing services.
            </p>
